The paper discusses privacy and tracking on the web, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The use of images for tracking also involves multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques. The paper also discusses the limitations of ad-blockers, which is related to systems and information (cs.SI). Finally, the paper uses image classification techniques, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV).
